%% ODH Model Controller - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>(istio-system)
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>HTTPS TLS Passthrough
    participant Predictor as KServe Predictor Pod<br/>8012/TCP mTLS

    participant MMRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>(isvc namespace)
    participant ModelMesh as modelmesh-serving<br/>8008/8443 TCP

    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>(3 replicas)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>OpenShift Monitoring

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 1: KServe InferenceService External Access
        Client->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Router->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Passthrough
        Route->>IstioGW: HTTPS<br/>TLS Passthrough
        IstioGW->>Predictor: HTTP/8012<br/>mTLS (Istio PeerAuth)
        Predictor-->>IstioGW: Inference Response
        IstioGW-->>Router: Response
        Router-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,ModelMesh: Flow 2: ModelMesh InferenceService (Auth Enabled)
        Client->>Router: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
        Router->>MMRoute: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS Reencrypt
        MMRoute->>ModelMesh: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (auth-delegator)
        ModelMesh-->>Router: Inference Response
        Router-->>Client: HTTPS Response
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Storage Config Aggregation
        Note right of Controller: Watches secrets with<br/>opendatahub.io/managed label
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Secret Watch Event<br/>(data connection created/updated)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update storage-config<br/>Secret (aggregated credentials)
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Prometheus,Controller: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext
        Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller Metrics
        Note right of Prometheus: Via ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor
        Prometheus->>Predictor: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086 (caikit) plaintext<br/>HTTP/3000 (tgis) plaintext
        Predictor-->>Prometheus: Inference Metrics
    end
